<window>
1. Click the button, you should see the content is shown with an animation(appear)
<separator/>
2. Click the button again, you should see the content is hidden with an animation(fade out)
<div id="t" visible="false"
action="onshow: anima.appear(#{self},4000); onhide:
anima.fade(#{self},4000)">
<div><!-- the 2nd div is optional but sometimes it looks better
with it -->
<groupbox>
<caption label="slide down"/>
Hi <textbox/>
</groupbox>
When? <datebox/>
</div>
</div>
<button label="toggle" onClick="t.visible = !t.visible"/>
</window>
